    <p>For inquiries regarding this privacy policy or any privacy-related concerns, please contact us at <a href="mailto:jimcampbell355@gmail.com">jimcampbell355@gmail.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Conclusion</h2>

    <p>By using Gmail Cleaner, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy. We are committed to maintaining the highest standards of privacy and security for our users.</p>
